mir | عامر","text":"Yeess.. except paav is no good","time":"Dec 11, 2023 10:53 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Will go through it","time":"Dec 11, 2023 10:56 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"And replace it slowly","time":"Dec 11, 2023 10:56 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yess ma'am","time":"Dec 11, 2023 10:57 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"And Ramadan will be coming too very soon","time":"Dec 11, 2023 10:57 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"At that my house becomes the hub of fried items 😂","time":"Dec 11, 2023 10:58 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"👍"},{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"😂"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Right","time":"Dec 11, 2023 10:59 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I am scared too","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:01 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"My mum only makes onion Bhajji","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:01 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Cannot demand nothing","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:02 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"It's good tho..can't stop myself from eating these","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:02 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Last time I thought of making smoothie for iftar and have only fruits..but idk how my hands were going only for fried items..so, I stopped making smoothie 😶","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:04 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I saw a site where they have frozen of these seekh and all","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:04 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Like the readymade stuff which u just need to fry?","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:05 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Yep","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:06 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yess..you can get it in Licious","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:06 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"*on","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:07 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"It’s too expensive","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:07 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"These ones are kind off like wholesale","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:07 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"So has better prices","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:07 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yupp I know..not worth it too","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:07 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Ohh...not sure then ..was it online","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:08 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"👍"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"My ex colleague told me","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:10 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"They bought it as well","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:10 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Was good","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:10 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"It would be a good option for me","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:10 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Okkay","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:10 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yesss...you can try smoothies too ..healthy and filling along with fruits","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:11 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Last Ramadan was the best spiritual based","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:12 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Yet I opened the fasts mostly alone","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:12 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"You used to be at work?","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:12 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Yepp","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:12 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I have been at work mostly since I started to work","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:13 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"But I used to have sis or mum with me","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:13 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Okkay..","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:14 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"You are working from home many years now","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:14 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"At work?","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:15 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Like I worked with my mum very firstly","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:16 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"It was like a factory work","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:16 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"And then I joined my sis in the clinic","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:16 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"And now I am alone","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:16 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Okkayy, got it","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:17 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Yepp","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:18 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"How was yours ?","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:18 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Last Ramadan I used to go to the office for 2 days ..some other person used to give me company during iftaar","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:19 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"}]},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Before that when I was in Bangalore, that was a struggle..I had to buy stuff daily from outside and I got sick because of that","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:20 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"It must have been fustrating","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:21 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"First 2 years when i was in hostel, they used to arrange iftaar for all the Muslims but when we got out and rented a flat..it baceme difficult..we were 4 of us ..2 Muslim and 2 nin Muslims..we didn't have much time to make stuff because college and everything..si that was the only way","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:22 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"😢"}]},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yess..it was...but we got used to it..","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:23 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I always find it hard to imagine how you must have been away and felt in those times","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:24 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Like being alone is the hardest thing, being with a crowd of you own people sometimes leaves you feeling lonely yet being alone in a different place is …","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:25 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yess... rightly said ...it was difficult..in college to I was fine cause I was used to hostel Life so living alone didn't really bothered..but in school it was nightmare ..I was like 8 or 9 years old at that time","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:28 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I literally used to cry every night...the saddest I used to be when I would see other parents coming and visiting their child but mine never did","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:29 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"😢"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"It hurts bad, when you get hurt by your own people trust strips away and everthing seems temporary","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:31 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"And the thought that nobody will stay long enough seeps deep in the mind","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:32 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Exactly.. especially by someone who is supposed to be there for you","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:33 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"That's why I am afraid to get too close to anyone..even my parents..it's not like I hate my parents..but I don't get that from inside cause I have never felt that way when I needed it","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:35 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"😔"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I was closer to my father","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:36 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Did you try getting in touch with him or did he","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:37 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I was younger when we came to Kerala and had not been with him much","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:38 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"When called he was like any other father","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:38 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"But when I returned my mothers stories were proven. He was the epitome of toxic masculinity","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:39 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"He was good at gaslighting and manipulating his way thorough.","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:39 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"But I still believed him","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:41 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I mean the people who manipulate things are difficult to understand..they put different side of them to different people depending on how they want others to perceive them..","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:45 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I once saw my friends father","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:45 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I saw them simply saying bye to each other as her father was going on work","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:46 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"And realised it was this easy","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:46 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"And chose to let him go","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:46 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"It hurts but you will be knowing him way better than others do and if you know how it's and then letting go can be good if you will see things from a larger perspective....I know me or anyone saying things won't understand how one feels..but you gotta be super strong and brave to come to terms with such things...and you are doing extremely well and you will continue to do so..I know it","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:51 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I have to come to a better understanding, I do not suppress my feeling about him. I speak about him when I miss him. He is not hidden part of life","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:56 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Just not pretty enough to remember","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:56 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I get that...and nothing wrong in it","time":"Dec 11, 2023 11:57 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I had somewhat similar equation with my father..he didn't like me when I was child..he rarely used to talk to me..like in years...things started changing from 2014..I don't have a single memory before that except some traumatic ones","time":"Dec 11, 2023 12:00 pm","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"👍"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"🥺","time":"Dec 11, 2023 12:02 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I am literally crying now","time":"Dec 11, 2023 12:02 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Don't..it's fine","time":"Dec 11, 2023 12:03 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I look so ugly when I cry","time":"Dec 11, 2023 12:03 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I should never cry infront of you","time":"Dec 11, 2023 12:03 pm","kind":"msg"}]